sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant VS as Istio VirtualService
    participant Activator as Knative Activator<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Agent as Agent Sidecar<br/>9081/TCP HTTP
    participant ModelServer as Model Server Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant EventSink as Event Sink<br/>80/443 HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over Client,EventSink: Flow 1: Model Deployment (InferenceService Creation)

    Client->>Gateway: kubectl apply InferenceService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>Gateway: Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    Gateway->>Gateway: Webhook Server 9443/TCP<br/>Validate/Mutate
    Gateway->>Gateway: Controller watches CR
    Gateway->>Gateway: Controller creates<br/>Knative Service + Istio VS

    Note over Client,EventSink: Flow 2: Model Loading (Storage Initialization)

    ModelServer->>ModelServer: storage-initializer init container starts
    ModelServer->>S3: GET model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM/Secret Key
    S3-->>ModelServer: Model files
    ModelServer->>ModelServer: Write to /mnt/models<br/>(shared volume)
    ModelServer->>ModelServer: Model server container starts<br/>Load from /mnt/models
    ModelServer->>Gateway: Update readiness probe

    Note over Client,EventSink: Flow 3: Inference Request (Serverless Mode)

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
    Gateway->>VS: Route to InferenceService
    VS->>Activator: HTTP/80 mTLS<br/>Service Identity
    Activator->>Agent: Forward request<br/>HTTP/9081
    Agent->>ModelServer: Proxy to model server<br/>HTTP/8080 (localhost)
    ModelServer->>ModelServer: Run inference
    ModelServer-->>Agent: Prediction result
    Agent-->>Activator: Response
    Agent->>EventSink: Log request/response<br/>HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Activator-->>VS: Response
    VS-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON prediction<br/>HTTPS/443

    Note over Client,EventSink: Flow 4: Multi-Model InferenceGraph

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/infer<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
    Gateway->>Gateway: Router Pod<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
    Gateway->>ModelServer: Model A Service<br/>HTTP/80 mTLS
    Gateway->>ModelServer: Model B Service<br/>HTTP/80 mTLS
    ModelServer-->>Gateway: Combined results
    Gateway-->>Client: Final response<br/>HTTPS/443
